{
  "text": "Before the release of ChatGPT, educators have already warned of compromises to academic integrity with the widespread usage of machine translators (MTs), such as Google Translate, and digital writing assistants (DWAs), such as Grammarly (Dehouche 2021; Roe et al. 2023).",
